Hello

01:06:14.930 --> 01:06:17.194
Anybody lose this?

01:06:17.299 --> 01:06:19.267
Hello?

01:06:19.368 --> 01:06:21.928
This your dog?

01:06:25.240 --> 01:06:29.199
