Where's David?

01:06:47.029 --> 01:06:49.395
Can you help me find David?

01:06:52.034 --> 01:06:54.400
I have to find David

01:06:55.804 --> 01:06:59.171
Are you taking me to David?

01:07:47.522 --> 01:07:50.685
Could you kind of shoot me
