01:08:40.670 --> 01:08:43.036
<i>We are alive...</i>

01:08:43.139 --> 01:08:46.973
<i>and this is a celebration...</i>

01:08:47.077 --> 01:08:49.011
<i>of life!</i>

01:08:49.112 --> 01:08:52.206
<i>And this is commitment...</i>

01:08:52.314 --> 01:08:56.684
<i>to a truly human future!</i>

