about this?

01:09:56.479 --> 01:09:59.846
- The bear told me.
- I told her

01:10:03.353 --> 01:10:06.345
Yeah! Yeah!

01:10:09.225 --> 01:10:13.127
Would you be so kind and
shut down my pain receivers?

01:10:20.537 --> 01:10:22.528
Why is this happening?

01:10:22.639 --> 01:10:25.631
History repeats itself

01:10:25.742 --> 01:10:29.405
It's the rite of blood
and electricity

01:10:29.512 --> 01:10:33.346
So, when the opportunities avail
themselves, they pick away at us...

01:10:33.450 --> 01:10:37.750
cutting back our numbers so they
can maintain numerical superiority

01:10:41.858 --> 01:10:44.554
My time, is it up already?

01:10:44.661 --> 01:10:47.653
- Good-bye, everyone.
- Keep me safe, keep me safe, keep me safe!

01:10:47.764 --> 01:10:49.891
